55.4	Bane_(comics)	Bane (comics)	Bane is a fictional character who appears in comic books published by DC Comics. The character first appeared in Batman: Vengeance of Bane #1 (January 1993), and was created by Chuck Dixon, Doug Moench, and Graham Nolan. Bane has been one of Batman's more physically and intellectually powerful foes. A virtually unstoppable juggernaut, he is best known for breaking Batman's back in the "Knightfall" story arc. IGN's list of the Top 100 Comic Book Villains of All Time ranked Bane as #34.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/c/cb/Bane_DC_Comics_Character.png/250px-Bane_DC_Comics_Character.png
